.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, february, december, november, july
City: nizza, hannover, marseilles, paris, london
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cycling, biathlon, weightlifting, rugby, handball
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, milk, orange-juice, water
5 different pets are kept: dog, fox, zebra, horse, snails

1. the person traveling to nizza is the person who's birthday is in march
2. the person traveling to hannover is the owner of the dog
3. the person drinking coffee is the person who's birthday is in february
4. the person traveling to marseilles is the person drinking tea
5. the person who's birthday is in february is to the right of the person who's birthday is in december
6. the person who's sport is cycling is the owner of the snails
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person who's birthday is in november
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the person traveling to paris is on the far left
10. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the owner of the fox
11. the person who's sport is biathlon is to the left or right of the owner of the horse
12. the person who's sport is rugby is the person drinking orange-juice
13. the person traveling to london is the person who's sport is handball
14. the person traveling to paris is to the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| City	|   paris	|    marseilles	|     nizza	|    hannover	|    london	|
| Birthday		|    november	|      july	|      march	|     december	|     february	|
| Beverage	|     water	|      tea	|      milk	| orange-juice	|     coffee	|
| Sport		|     biathlon	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| rugby	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     fox	|     horse	|     snails	|     dog	|     zebra	|
